  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Behold the sights of the West, all done in a Hidden Object style. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play over 30 fun minigames, all connected to the West! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up fun facts about the region! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Comes with wallpapers and a full soundtrack. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maximize your vacation with Unlimited Mode!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>Collector's Edition</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 more chapters </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 CE-exclusive Hidden Object scenes!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the rich history and culture of the Western United States and discover its hidden treasures in this new hidden object game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767140/extras/c1ab31a4b98bc6c628905638c4973b7f.poster.avif?t=1729486755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767140/extras/c1ab31a4b98bc6c628905638c4973b7f.webm?t=1729486755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767140/extras/c1ab31a4b98bc6c628905638c4973b7f.mp4?t=1729486755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along your journey, you'll encounter fascinating fun facts about the iconic Western locations you visit, from the towering peaks of Yosemite National Park, the beautiful Grand Canyon, and iconic Santa Monica Pier. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767140/extras/6a3fcbeed57da52eb2875ec54739dd8b.poster.avif?t=1729486755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767140/extras/6a3fcbeed57da52eb2875ec54739dd8b.webm?t=1729486755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767140/extras/6a3fcbeed57da52eb2875ec54739dd8b.mp4?t=1729486755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With stunning visuals and engaging gameplay, our game is the ultimate Western adventure for players of all ages.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the rich history and culture of the Western United States and discover its hidden treasures in this new hidden object game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767140/extras/c1ab31a4b98bc6c628905638c4973b7f.poster.avif?t=1729486755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767140/extras/c1ab31a4b98bc6c628905638c4973b7f.webm?t=1729486755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767140/extras/c1ab31a4b98bc6c628905638c4973b7f.mp4?t=1729486755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along your journey, you'll encounter fascinating fun facts about the iconic Western locations you visit, from the towering peaks of Yosemite National Park, the beautiful Grand Canyon, and iconic Santa Monica Pier. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767140/extras/6a3fcbeed57da52eb2875ec54739dd8b.poster.avif?t=1729486755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767140/extras/6a3fcbeed57da52eb2875ec54739dd8b.webm?t=1729486755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767140/extras/6a3fcbeed57da52eb2875ec54739dd8b.mp4?t=1729486755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With stunning visuals and engaging gameplay, our game is the ultimate Western adventure for players of all ages.</p>",
